Class PbMessageValueRemediationParameterStringBuilderIetf

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ietf.nea.pb.message.util.PbMessageValueRemediationParameterStringBuilderIetf
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PbMessageSubValueBuilder<PbMessageValueRemediationParameterString>, PbMessageValueRemediationParameterStringBuilder

    public class PbMessageValueRemediationParameterStringBuilderIetf
extends Object
implements PbMessageValueRemediationParameterStringBuilder
    Builder to build a TNCCS message string remediation parameter value compliant to RFC 5793. It evaluates the given values and can be used in a fluent way.
